&apos;s subscription to </div><div class="t m1167 x5d h2d y1832 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">each library during 1901 for $1.00. This is </div><div class="t m736 xc6 h29 y6be ff6 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Send one tract </div><div class="t m850 xc6 h29 y1fe3 ff6 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">each week.&quot; </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
